OJS 3.3.0.6 Release Notes
Git tag: 3_3_0-6

Release date: June 1, 2021
===========================

Configuration Changes (config.inc.php)
--------------------------------------

New parameter added to avoid sending any email (when it's Off) for debugging purposes.
- email.allow_send_email

New parameter added to reduce the number of logs when the parameter "debug.show_stacktrace" is On.
The logs for emails are not shown when the parameter below is On.
- debug.hide_email_stacktrace

3.3.0-6 Build
-------------

- Migrated all user gossips into a contextual table that has been renamed private_notes.
